// v1.6 forward: `_dict_values<V>(Dict<String, V>) -> List<V>` now
// flows the value type through. A typed `List<Int>` slot accepts the
// result of `_dict_values` on a `Dict<String, Int>` source — pre-v1.6
// this returned `List<Any>` and required a coercion.
// EXPECTED: 0 × StaticTypeMismatch.
{
  Dict<String, Int> scores: { math: 100, art: 90 },
  List<Int> values: _dict_values(scores)
}
